{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 Here, you can create both Contact records and Phone records.\par
\par
In the case of Phone records, the program uses the Record ID to link the two sets of data. Magic uses the Node IDs in the background to create the proper XML.\par
\par
In the case of Contact records, they are all automatically linked to the Root, because that is the only level above.\par
